  "title": "Business Support Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for a proactive Business Support Executive to assist with day-to-day administrative and operational support across business functions. This role is suitable for individuals who are organised, adaptable, and comfortable working in a structured environment. No prior experience is required as training and guidance will be provided.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Organise and manage schedules, documentation, and records to support business teams’ daily operations</li><li>Communicate clearly with internal teams and external parties to facilitate smooth information flow</li><li>Prepare basic reports and maintain accurate data records to support decision-making</li><li>Follow up on assigned tasks to ensure timely completion and uninterrupted business processes</li><li>Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned to support operational needs</li><li>Use basic computer skills to operate email, messaging apps, and spreadsheets for daily tasks</li><li>Work independently and collaboratively within a team to achieve business objectives</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Willingness to learn and adapt to new tasks and processes</li></ul>",
